{"tid":542573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"MH系列終於返嚟 但我已經返唔到嚟","createTime":"2018-01-27T15:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T06:54:55.000Z","uid":71379,"like":44,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"34d586168a8db93fae9eee1d74101aac8bcf97e8","tid":542573,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"記得細個由MH2G玩起<br />\n嗰陣有得用外掛貓 <br />\n每場跑到去俾隻貓扑兩野就完場<br />\n鐘意就換走隻貓 靠自己打<br />\n砌好套靚裝 戰戰兢兢去打老山龍 老山蟹<br />\n步步為營 所有野都要計好曬 <br />\n打到最後一秒手汗都出埋 先知勝負<br />\n嗰陣每日打到冇電叉住玩 玩下玩下就一日<br />\n出街都係約埋啲朋友玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到新出MH3 仲未有繁中補丁冇外掛<br />\n用累積嘅經驗由頭靠自己去攻略呢隻game<br />\n無論係搵草 捧蛋 打大怪 打細怪<br />\n靠自己去完成每個任務都好有滿足感<br />\n睇住裝備慢慢變強 隻貓慢慢變勁<br />\n就好似經歷過一段人生咁<br />\n嗰陣嘅自己 打機會開心 有成功感<br />\n<br />\n直到好似3G好似移植去任記<br />\n嗰個時候冇打算換機<br />\n（嗰陣覺得男人就應該玩Ps）<br />\n只期待佢終有一日回家<br />\nMH嘅生涯就喺度結束<br />\n手提機嘅旅程都漸漸結束<br />\n慢慢進入玩電腦Online game嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n到而家大咗<br />\n連電腦都少玩<br />\n只係玩下啲連線嘅手機game<br />\n唔係唔開心 只係冇咗以前嘅感覺<br />\n好似只係無目的地消磨時間<br />\n<br />\nSwitch出咗冇興趣<br />\n到MH終於返到Play station<br />\n但而家嘅我<br />\n已經冇曬一齊作戰嘅戰友<br />\n冇咗打機嘅熱情同時間<br />\n再冇耐性打完每場掘石收割<br />\n再冇耐性為咗合一件裝打同一場好多次<br />\n再冇耐性承擔會輸嘅風險用成個鐘打隻大怪 然後輸咗再接再厲<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 芒亨你終於返嚟 但我已經返唔到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e886f3d46baedcda3edbbc9f778fac3b0fc026e","tid":542573,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"Ro wow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f039baa72b33a0ba15b5cd913307680098f86719","tid":542573,"uid":18107,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"你有無比錢買過隻game?"},{"pid":"90a3a934e9fb8d4d07a6401620bceb30d94ac761","tid":542573,"uid":28335,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"f039baa72b33a0ba15b5cd913307680098f86719","tid":542573,"uid":18107,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"你有無比錢買過隻game?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"有冇買同個主題有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a390e47eb36acb3e2302dd22779ba4339fca9cfd","tid":542573,"uid":152437,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7067f1f12e66fb38ac00dce0e8bb21c8d636a459","tid":542573,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9759733b8a2a6c0f6744f1093a02010dafa57e2c","tid":542573,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db4f0190f2bd06af9b7905b306a3aa248c6991e","tid":542573,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"佢仍然係佢<br />\n<br />\n但你已經唔係你"},{"pid":"701b647961aebac21abc6b77fb8056ced65ecf5e","tid":542573,"uid":77267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"玩都未玩就係度作文，去r機打返兩三場你再評論啦"},{"pid":"0e800f6819a4598057aa03fe2cebd0a15584ae40","tid":542573,"uid":31215,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"見D偽hunter fans 就好笑<br />\n任記mon hunt 唔玩都好意思話自己鍾意mon hun<br />\nsony 死忠就sony死忠啦"},{"pid":"0dd2d512a16642ffaa71186b38f5e80bdeb69818","tid":542573,"uid":36026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"依加一可以坐定定打機就已經會擔心第二日既工作<br />\n我諗可能要到我退休先可以好好享受遊戲"},{"pid":"cc240f1508c5ffeb1114c4d35daece715e02cdba","tid":542573,"uid":74970,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"男人就應該玩ps,仲講到回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死<br />\n咪又係乜野hit就走去玩乜，唔係真係鍾意打機"},{"pid":"c72da1a6cbba9a3289872606868517095afe